summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Ella S. Henderson and J. E. Henderson, her husband, to The City of Seattle, dated November 4th, A. D. 1909, to the following described real property, situated in King County, State of Washington, particularly described as follows: All of Lot Fifteen (15), Block Fourteen (14), Front Street Cable Addition to the City of Seattle, except the portion thereof condemned by The City of Seattle for Queen Anne Boulevard, under Ordinance No. 16790 of said city.
